  "text": "Plates with growing seedlings were moved to the image acquisition room once a day, from DAS3 (corresponding to the first day after germination) for 5 d until DAS7, scanned and, after imaging, returned immediately to the growth chamber. The root traits were quantified by high-throughput plugin BRAT including manual quality control step, as described in [CITATION_1] .",
